Mainspringror project - multiclient CMS for managing videos, users, comments, ratings

Restful resources for CRUD operations on clients, their videos and their users with predictable urls.

Security through obfuscation, no sequential integer ids in urls for clients or videos or users.  

Session authentication before_filter on all controllers, no casual browsers can access data.

clients/x/users/login_or_create?username=abc&location=xyz - allows client's user an entry point to login as a user (or create a new account if doesn't exist).

login_or_create?... goto=forward_to_url_that_is_cgi_escapeHTML - after entry point, forward user to CMS page (allows real bookmarking)

clients/x/videos/search?terms search within client videos matching search terms
